@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> DisplayTime : waiting for input
DisplayTime --> PowerSelection : select power level
PowerSelection --> TimeSetting : set cooking time
TimeSetting --> Cooking : start cooking
Cooking --> [*] : door opened
Cooking --> CancelCooking : cancel cooking
CancelCooking --> DisplayTime : return to display time
DisplayTime --> Idle : wait for next use
@enduml
